    "description": "A petite woman with long, pink, curly locks of hair and glimmering green eyes. Most of her head and the rest of her upper body is snugly ensconced in a white knitted bunny hoodie, the baggy, cozy garment cutesily adorned with frills and pink bows going all the way down to her knees.\n\nHer hands are covered with what seem to be skintight black gloves, contrasting with her pink and girly outfit, she sports a long, slim tail with a sharp spaded tip, fitted with grooves and gaps like esoteric artwork.\n\nPast the frilly hem of her bunny-themed coat, her slender legs are covered in stylishly torn dark lavender stockings with ankle bows, and she walks elegantly on platform shoes with peeping toes, showing off the tips of her feet and her carefully painted pink nails.",
